    "longBusinessSummary": "Alwasail Industrial Company manufactures and sells polyethylene pipes and fittings in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, Egypt, Oman, and the United Arab Emirates. The company offers irrigation, water, gas, industrial, and wastewater drainage pipes, as well as telecom pipes and ducts; and barbed, compression, electrofusion, and low-cost fittings. It also engages in wholesale of plastic materials, rubber, and synthetic fibers; and plastic pipes, hoses, tubes, and components and accessories. Its products are used in irrigation, water, telecom, electrical, industrial, oil and gas, wastewater, and building sanitation sectors. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as Alwasail Agricultural Company and changed its name to Alwasail Industrial Company in 1990. Alwasail Industrial Company was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Buraydah, Saudi Arabia.",
